ahm | language = de | publisher = kicker.de | accessdate = 23 May 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[2015\u201316 FC Bayern Munich season|2015\u201316]]||26||1||6||0||12||0||1||0||45||1||<ref>{{cite web|title=Philipp Lahm|url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/1-bundesliga/2015-16/bayern-muenchen-14/26870/spieler_philipp-lahm.html|website=kicker.de|publisher=kicker|access-date = 21 May 2016 |language=German}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/startseite/d-supercup-fb-1/2015/1/2841005/spielbericht_vfl-wolfsburg-24_bayern-muenchen-14.html | title = Joker Bendtner ist zweimal zur Stelle | language = de | website = kicker.de | date = 1 August 2015 | access-date = 1 August 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[2016\u201317 FC Bayern Munich season|2016\u201317]]||26||1||4||1||7||0||1||0||38||2||<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/startseite/d-supercup-fb-1/2016/1/3303617/spielbericht_borussia-dortmund-17_bayern-muenchen-14.html | title = Im zweiten Anlauf: Vidal beschert Bayern den ersten Titel | language = de | website = kicker.de | date = 14 August 2016 | access-date = 14 August 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/1-bundesliga/2016-17/bayern-muenchen-14/26870/spieler_philipp-lahm.html | title = Philipp Lahm | language = de | website = kicker.de | access-date = 20 May 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Totals!!332!!12!!54!!3!!117!!1!!14!!0!!517!!16!!\u2014\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[VfB Stuttgart|Stuttgart]] (loan)||[[2003\u201304 VfB Stuttgart season|2003\u201304]]||rowspan=\"2\"|Bundesliga||31||1||1||0||7||0||1||0||40||1||<ref>{{cite web|title=Philipp Lahm|url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/2003-04/26870/vereinsspieler_philipp-lahm.html|publisher=kicker|accessdate=17 February 2014|language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[2004\u201305 VfB Stuttgart season|2004\u201305]]||22||1||2||0||6||1||1||0||31||1||<ref>{{cite web|title=Philipp Lahm|url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/vereine/2004-05/26870/vereinsspieler_philipp-lahm.html|publisher=kicker|accessdate=17 February 2014|language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Totals!!53!!2!!3!!0!!13!!1!!2!!0!!71!!3!!\u2014\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career totals!!448!!17!!58!!3!!130!!2!!16!!0!!652!!22!!\u2014\n|}\n*1.{{note|a}}Includes [[DFB-Pokal|German Cup]].\n*2.{{note|a}}Includes [[UEFA Champions League]] and [[UEFA Europa League|UEFA Cup]].\n*3.{{note|a}}Includes [[DFL-Ligapokal|German League Cup]], [[DFL-Supercup|German Super Cup]], [[UEFA Super Cup]], and [[FIFA Club World Cup]].\n\n===International===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!colspan=3|[[Germany national football team|Germany]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n| 2004 || 15 || 1\n|-\n| 2005 || 0 || 0\n|-\n| 2006 || 15 || 1\n|-\n| 2007 || 7 || 0\n|-\n| 2008 || 15 || 1\n|-\n| 2009 || 11 || 0\n|-\n| 2010 || 12 || 1\n|-\n| 2011 || 10 || 0\n|-\n| 2012 || 10 || 1\n|-\n| 2013 || 9 || 0\n|-\n| 2014 || 9 || 0\n|-\n! Total || 113 || 5\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n''Scores and results table. Germany's goal tally first:''\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: left;\" align=center\n|+ '''Philipp Lahm: International Goals'''<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.dfb.de/index.php?id=500397&action=showPlayer&full=1&liga=Nationalmannschaft&vorname=&nachname=Lahm&cHash=0604488660 | title = Philipp Lahm's full international stats | publisher = dfb.de | accessdate =26 June 2008}}</ref>\n\n! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1. || 28 April 2004 || [[Stadionul Giulesti]], [[Bucharest]], Romania || {{fb|Romania}} || 1\u20135 || 1\u20135 || [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n|-\n| 2. || 9 June 2006 || [[Allianz Arena|WM-Stadion M\u00fcnchen]], Munich, Germany || {{fb|Costa Rica}} || 1\u20130 || 4\u20132 || [[2006 FIFA World Cup]]\n|-\n| 3. || 25 June 2008 || [[St. Jakob Park]], [[Basel]], Switzerland || {{fb|Turkey}} || 3\u20132 || 3\u20132 || [[UEFA Euro 2008